            <title>[LU-8691] ha.sh improvements: add mdtest, add simultaneous victim nodes failover</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8691</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Seagate customers use mdtest load on failover/failback tests and perform failover of several osts simultaneously.&lt;br/&gt;
Proposed patch adds:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;mdtest mpi load;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;ha_simultaneous mode, which allows to reboot&lt;br/&gt;
  victim nodes simultaneously.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
